_sText:
So I felt like making another deathrun map. A few hours later, here is the results.

20 Traps
45 CT Spawns
2 T Spawns

And a fun little rocket launcher at the end of the map. It seems to glitch out every now and then (it will be facing the wrong direction), however it is still fully functional. Just looks weird.

Any bugs/suggestions, feel free to post.

*4th Version made just to balance some traps.
